  "texts": [
    "This signifies that with this model, the correct identification of good fits and false positives is very well balanced.Good Fit Description Bad Fit Description Observations• High Match Cases: In cases where resumes overlapped significantly with the skills required in the job description, the system was accurate in its prediction of a good fit.",
    "• Low Match Cases: For resumes lacking the necessary skills or having content unrelated to the job description, the system accurately raised an alarm about the mismatch.",
    "• Semantic Similarity Limitation: Though the cosine similarity produced an appropriate level of general textual similarity, it only marginally reflected relevance to the competency.",
    "In some cases, resumes with general textual similarity had considerable overlap in skills.",
    "Challenges and Limitations• Skill Extraction: The fixed list-based extraction of skills likely omitted important skills that were simply not specifically mentioned in the job description."
